Changelog
=========

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

1.0.1 (2019-05-10):
  - Changed project URLs.

1.0.0 (2019-05-03):
  - Added CHANGELOG file.
  - Added help link to MediaWiki.org.
  - Added link to toolbar at Special:Contributions.
  - Fixed user permissions: only logged-in users can display the special page.

0.1.0 (2019-05-01):
  - New extension to obtain basic info about IP address from the WHOIS
    registries.
  - Basic extension structure, which can request a WHOIS report via telnet.
